resource/Mandy_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandy_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"score\": 0.9722522670736626, \"rank\": 0.02853963484765122, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\"}, {\"begin\": 1704, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999739920816572, \"rank\": 2.5916489547450758e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been nerve racking, but so much fun.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been fantastic watching Kieran after missing out on Tokyo and we are super proud of him.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"score\": 0.9722522670736626, \"rank\": 0.02853963484765122, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\"}, {\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9998753331341688, \"rank\": 0.00011015275571731082, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Bicester community have been great, we have had so many lovely messages of support, that has meant so much - thank you Bicester.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bicester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49